title: GPSC Notification 2026 - Apply Online for 07 Assistant Engineer, Executive Engineer Posts
description: The Gujarat Public Service Commission (GPSC) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 07 Assistant Engineer, Executive Engineer, and Deputy Executive Engineer Jobs. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their B.E./B.
